CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E2E3_stage1_final AS SELECT MIN(E2_s) AS EXPR$0 FROM E2E3_stage1_2 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E3E5_stage1_final WHERE E2E3_stage1_2.E2_d=E3E5_stage1_final.E5_s AND E2E3_stage1_2.E3_s=E3E5_stage1_final.E3_s)
SELECT * FROM E2E3_stage1_final"
